OL,3,CCaroline Glachan: Trio guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering schoolgirl found dead in
OL,5,Criver 27 years ago
OL,7,FTwo men and one woman have been found
OL,8,Fguilty of murdering a schoolgirl in
OL,9,FWest Dunbartonshire 27 years ago.
OL,11,FThe body of 14-year-old Caroline
OL,12,FGlachan was found on the banks of the
OL,13,FRiver Leven on August 25, 1996.
OL,15,FOn Thursday, Robert O'Brien, 45,
OL,16,FAndrew Kelly and Donna Marie Brand,
OL,17,Fboth 44, were convicted of her murder,
OL,18,Fafter a trial at the High Court in
OL,19,FGlasgow.
